name: Feb 10th 2021 Rifff
description: This is one of the latest ‘Rifffs’ I created using Endlesss.fm, the live music creation platform I founded. Making music on Endlesss unfolds as an endless flow of Rifffs, each one a remix of the previous, building up a complete history of musical creativity going back to the very first Rifff in a jam.   Over the coming weeks I will release further selected Rifffs from my Endlesss solo jam, going back in time to the first complete Rifff which I created on April 24th 2019.
